        <articleContents><![CDATA[<p>Lipsum is a free and useful Lorem Ipsum generator that you can make use of in your projects. As a freelance designer, you might already be aware of the value of the Lorem Ipsum text. Even though it is centuries old, Lorem Ipsum is still very popular as a placeholder text to help designers showcase their designs to clients. Such placeholder text aids in visualization.</p>
<p>However, that does not mean that placeholder texts should be boring.<span> </span><a href="http://lipsum.com/">Lipsum</a><span> </span>fixes just that — it uses 200+ Latin words to generate modern, readable and simple Lorem Ipsum.</p>
<p>Go ahead and give it a spin for your projects! And if Lipsum does not seem right to you, check out some more<span> </span><a href="https://www.designbombs.com/hysterical-lorem-ipsum-generators/">free Lorem Ipsum generators</a>.</p>
<p>Like Lipsum? Share your views in the comments below!</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9660" src="http://webresourcesdepot.com/wp-content/uploads/lorem-ipsum.png" alt="Lorem Ipsum Generators" /></p>]]></articleContents>
