        <projectContents><![CDATA[<div id="post-1899" class="post">
<div>
<p>I'm sure better tools exist, but hey, quick and dirty is faster:</p>
<pre>const total = document.documentElement.innerHTML.length;
const scripts = Array.from(document.getElementsByTagName('script')).reduce((total, e) =&gt; total += e.innerHTML.length, 0);
const styles = Array.from(document.getElementsByTagName('style')).reduce((total, e) =&gt; total += e.innerHTML.length, 0);
console.log("scripts", scripts, "styles:", styles, "html:", total - scripts - styles);
</pre>
<p>Running it quickly tells me where the wins can come from:</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1901" src="http://www.phpied.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/qss.png" alt="qss" width="650" /></p>
